gee maybe she agreed to the thing in the first place? We made a deal back 
when BK was basically on the verge of being killed, BK wouldnt be killed but 
when BK was out of the IGL she would be forced to return to the base and 
serve the Infecticons. Simple as that. She agreed to the terms now she has to 
follow through and on a slight note the control that is being issued is 
making BK head to the base as quickly as possible with as few obstacles as 
possible.
